{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"497a","heading":"Notification required for reduction or consolidation of dual-capable aircraft based in Europe","label":"497a Notification required for reduction or consolidation of dual-capable aircraft based in Europe","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptI/ch24","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Notification","label":"a .—Notification","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The reasons for such planned reduction or consolidation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Any effects of such planned reduction or consolidation on the extended deterrence mission of the United States.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The manner in which the military requirements of the North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) will continue to be met in light of such planned reduction or consolidation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A statement by the Secretary on the response of NATO to such planned reduction or consolidation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Whether there is any change in the force posture of the Russian Federation as a result of such planned reduction or consolidation, including with respect to the nonstrategic nuclear weapons of Russia that are within range of the member states of NATO.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Dual-capable Aircraft Defined","label":"b .—Dual-capable Aircraft Defined","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s497a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs497a%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In this section, the term “dual-capable aircraft” means aircraft that can perform both conventional and nuclear missions.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
